data.description: **Price Reduced** Don't miss out on the beautiful move in ready home that sits on a corner lot with almost an acre of flat useable land, completely fenced in backyard with accessible side gate entrance off of side street, bring your horses, farm animals or put in a big workshop, so many possibilities with this property including the possibility of sub-dividing (buyers to verify).  This home has 3 big bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a separate den/office/hobby or could be a 4th bedroom, nice kitchen with attached dining room and a big open living room/great room, a separate large laundry room/mud room.  There is a 2 car attached garage, a shed, a chicken coop and an open canvas backyard for you to design anyway you desire. This home has been well taken care of and shows very nicely. Home has been repainted on the inside and the out side trim was just repainted as well.
